comments: Doncic (DAL) deflects the pass towards the backcourt, where Holiday (NOP) legally gains possession of the ball.
Kleber (DAL) rests a forearm on Holiday's (NOP) body and does not deliver contact during his driving shot attempt.
Williams (NOP) makes marginal contact with Doncic's (DAL) body that does not affect his SQBR.
Doncic (DAL) gathers the ball and takes a legal two steps during the step back move on his jump shot attempt.
Wright (DAL) establishes himself in a legal screening position in Ball's (NOP) path and does not deliver contact.
Wright (DAL) makes marginal contact with Ingram (NOP) during his drive to the basket.
Wright (DAL) cleanly dislodges the ball from Hart (NOP) during the steal and any contact is considered incidental.
Holiday (NOP) and Kleber (DAL) engage and disengage during the rebound.
Kleber (DAL) and Williams (NOP) briefly engage and separate during the rebound.
Williams (NOP) commits a take foul on Finney-Smith (DAL).
Hart (NOP) commits a take foul on Wright (DAL).
